messages.message: if you just click open, it will take u to the general projects page which will allow u to create a project or choose an existing one for the side bar. if u click create, it will perform the action of creating a new project and redirect to that. If u click one of the projects that appear in the list, which are your recently opened projects, then it'll automatically go to that project

we’ve received feedback that these 2 buttons are confusing and have a ticket for this https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-3183

feel free to add your opinion there, if you’d like!
